            "name": "Chameleon Suit", 
            "weight": "5 lbs.", 
            "item_type": "light", 
            "text": "<p class=\"stat-block\">This suit of light woven-fiber armor covers the wearer from ankle to wrist and includes a hooded cowl. Its surface consists of millions of tiny, scale-like lenses and LED screens. When powered on, a chameleon suit analyzes its environment and generates digital camouflage. The wearer gains a +10 competence bonus on Stealth checks and can hide in plain sight (as a ranger in his favored terrain).</p>", 
